        <body>
      
		<pb n="1"/>
			<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Barcelona</placeName> <date>Janry 18th&#47;53</date></p>
			<p><addressee>Is Leeser Esqr.</addressee></p>
			<p><placeName>Philadpa</placeName></p>
          <p rend="indent(2)">Revd. Sir</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">Your valued note of the <date>15<hi rend="sup">th</hi></date> ulto. was recd &#38; duly no<lb/>ticed together with the proof sheet&#44; the size of which&#44; is more porta<lb/>ble than those your last edition&#44; excepting the quality of paper&#44; which<lb/> I found to be a little inferior&#59; my subscribers&#44; thro&#39; my organ&#44;<lb/> begs to have equal quality as the set of Parasa &#38; Prayer<lb/> Books which I hold here of your first Edition&#44; that is&#44; &#8220;with<lb/> no additional cost.&#8221;</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">I am truly sorry that I cannot prove of more<lb/> service to yr valued Periodical the Occident &#38; moreso to feel<lb/> the justice of your observation&#59; for tho&#39; few&#44; we &#40;they&#41; feel very<lb/> little interest in the genl. cause of Judaism&#8212;As far<lb/> as concerns myself&#44; I doubt not you will send or continue<lb/> sending the nos. &#38; inform me thro what channel you would<lb/> like them import to be remitted to you&#8212;<sic>wether</sic> Lag<add>&#63;</add><lb/> or <placeName>St Thomas</placeName>.<add>&#63;</add> Revd. Sr. I remain</p>
          <p rend="indent(5)">respectfully yours&#44;</p>
          <p rend="indent(5)"><persName role="author">Saml Piza</persName></p>
			<p>P.S. Please stamp no name on the covers of the set orderd<lb/> for <persName>A. H. Moro</persName>.</p>
		<pb n="2"/>
			<p>To the</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)"><addressee>Revd. Is. Leeser</addressee></p>
          <p rend="indent(3)"><placeName>Philada.</placeName></p>
			<p>care of <persName>Messr A. M.</persName></p>
          <p rend="indent(1)"><persName>Seixas &#38; Co.</persName></p>
          <p rend="indent(3)">via</p>
          <p rend="indent(3)"><placeName>La Gu<add>&#63;</add></placeName></p>
          
        </body>
